00:13:28.700 --> 00:13:31.590 align:middle line:10%
>> She intends to
change the future?

00:13:31.590 --> 00:13:32.390 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah, I guess.

00:13:32.390 --> 00:13:34.900 align:middle line:90%


00:13:34.900 --> 00:13:38.187 align:middle line:84%
>> So that's a fascinating
question because what

00:13:38.187 --> 00:13:40.270 align:middle line:84%
we're looking at here is
basically the mechanistic

00:13:40.270 --> 00:13:41.070 align:middle line:90%
universe.

00:13:41.070 --> 00:13:43.360 align:middle line:84%
And this is an
idea, a way to read

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.100 align:middle line:84%
the world, a picture
of the world that

00:13:45.100 --> 00:13:47.560 align:middle line:84%
has dominated since the time
of the scientific revolution

00:13:47.560 --> 00:13:48.700 align:middle line:90%
