00:13:56.980 --> 00:13:59.060 align:middle line:84%
and it's just kind
of ticking down.

00:13:59.060 --> 00:14:02.350 align:middle line:84%
And so in that view, everything
has its pre-determined causal

00:14:02.350 --> 00:14:05.200 align:middle line:84%
chain that makes it what it
