00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.170 align:middle line:90%
that--

00:14:06.170 --> 00:14:11.590 align:middle line:84%
that flat sort of, you know,
extended, determined future.

00:14:11.590 --> 00:14:12.610 align:middle line:90%
It's just there for you.

00:14:12.610 --> 00:14:13.410 align:middle line:90%
It's made for you.

00:14:13.410 --> 00:14:14.800 align:middle line:90%
