with the "Terminator" series

00:26:06.380 --> 00:26:09.670 align:middle line:84%
that they didn't go
full-bore B-movie,

00:26:09.670 --> 00:26:11.840 align:middle line:84%
that they kind of
started entertaining

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:12.990 align:middle line:90%
some of these higher ideas.

00:26:12.990 --> 00:26:13.580 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:26:13.580 --> 00:26:15.740 align:middle line:10%
>> I mean, they could have--
to be honest with you,

00:26:15.740 --> 00:26:17.570 align:middle line:10%
it would have been
a much bigger hit--

00:26:17.570 --> 00:26:19.870 align:middle line:10%
to have the terminators,
thousands of them,

00:26:19.870 --> 00:26:22.680 align:middle line:10%
unleashed on humanity and just
have this B-movie massacre,

00:26:22.680 --> 00:26:23.480 align:middle line:10%
right?

00:26:23.480 --> 00:26:24.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:26:24.280 --> 00:26:25.130 align:middle line:90%
>> And they didn't.

00:26:25.130 --> 00:26:27.671 align:middle line:84%
And I thought that was actually
kind of interesting that they

00:26:27.671 --> 00:26:28.970 align:middle line:90%
didn't resort to that.

00:26:28.970 --> 00:26:30.770 align:middle line:84%
They may in the
future, you know,

00:26:30.770 --> 00:26:32.630 align:middle line:84%
because that would be
a terrifying movie.

00:26:32.630 --> 00:26:34.790 align:middle line:84%
But it would not be an
intellectually challenging

00:26:34.790 --> 00:26:35.030 align:middle line:90%
movie.

00:26:35.030 --> 00:26:36.239 align:middle line:90%
It'd just be a horror film.

00:26:36.239 --> 00:26:38.030 align:middle line:10%
And so I was kind of
glad that they kind of

00:26:38.030 --> 00:26:41.300 align:middle line:10%
went into the more etheric
Skynet, the relationship

00:26:41.300 --> 00:26:43.520 align:middle line:10%
between man and machine.

00:26:43.520 --> 00:26:44.480 align:middle line:90%
>> Free will, you know.

00:26:44.480 --> 00:26:45.330 align:middle line:90%
>> And free will.

00:26:45.330 --> 00:26:49.730 align:middle line:84%
And it was just a-- it's
a worthy series, I think,

00:26:49.730 --> 00:26:50.730 align:middle line:90%
the whole series.

00:26:50.730 --> 00:26:52.970 align:middle line:84%
>> So in the more
recent installments,

00:26:52.970 --> 00:26:55.700 align:middle line:84%
the second to last,
"Terminator Salvation,"

00:26:55.700 --> 00:26:57.920 align:middle line:84%
this is where Christian
Bale comes into the picture.

00:26:57.920 --> 00:27:01.430 align:middle line:84%
