00:30:17.910 --> 00:30:19.590 align:middle line:10%
in the future for our progeny.

00:30:19.590 --> 00:30:20.940 align:middle line:90%
>> I highly recommend "Her."

00:30:20.940 --> 00:30:23.490 align:middle line:84%
That is a great film,
no doubt about it.

00:30:23.490 --> 00:30:28.050 align:middle line:84%
>> My final takeaway is that the
series is about human free will

00:30:28.050 --> 00:30:29.610 align:middle line:90%
versus technocracy.

00:30:29.610 --> 00:30:31.320 align:middle line:84%
I mean, that's the
overriding theme.

00:30:31.320 --> 00:30:34.830 align:middle line:84%
And the-- the third installment
and the fourth installment,

00:30:34.830 --> 00:30:38.040 align:middle line:84%
I think, explicitly make
reference to depopulation.

00:30:38.040 --> 00:30:41.352 align:middle line:84%
They talk about the plan of
the technocrats and their--

00:30:41.352 --> 00:30:44.700 align:middle line:84%
their evil offspring
and AI, right,

00:30:44.700 --> 00:30:48.420 align:middle line:84%
being there to ensure that
depopulation takes place.

00:30:48.420 --> 00:30:50.040 align:middle line:90%
And so I see it as-- as that.

00:30:50.040 --> 00:30:51.150 align:middle line:90%
I see it as Platonic.

00:30:51.150 --> 00:30:53.280 align:middle line:84%
I see it as a kind
of Gnostic sort

00:30:53.280 --> 00:30:57.060 align:middle line:84%
of being outside of the
pre-determined limits

00:30:57.060 --> 00:31:00.270 align:middle line:84%
and bounds of time through
some sort of rebellion

00:31:00.270 --> 00:31:01.900 align:middle line:90%
on the part of the human spirit.

00:31:01.900 --> 00:31:02.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:31:02.700 --> 00:31:05.620 align:middle line:90%
The demiurge is the Skynet.

00:31:05.620 --> 00:31:06.420 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:31:06.420 --> 00:31:08.310 align:middle line:90%
>> And the rebellion--

00:31:08.310 --> 00:31:11.640 align:middle line:84%
the rebellion among
the Sophianic masses

00:31:11.640 --> 00:31:14.310 align:middle line:84%
is coming through John
