00:31:15.520 --> 00:31:15.900 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:31:15.900 --> 00:31:18.510 align:middle line:84%
>> So the whole thing does have
a kind of a Gnostic overlay

00:31:18.510 --> 00:31:22.770 align:middle line:84%
